data.description: Lake front home with approximately 2400 sq ft and large backyard. Home offers so much potential for next owner with large spacious kitchen,  extra large primary suite with 3 walk-in closets, wonderful flex room with high ceilings and water view, covered back patio that could be converted into screen porch or other living space. The 2 car garage has been converted into living space and storage space. Wonderful solar panels convey to new owner at no additional cost. Great time to get into house like this to start building equity. Please note sellers are in the process of moving, so the home is being packed up and getting ready for the new owner .
